{"tid":1723313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動討論，打機撚入] 打機建立完據點，下一步係咩？","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:58:44.000Z","uid":144113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a262721b3c954eb031554dfbf65097b9661a1e19","tid":1723313,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:03:52.000Z","msg":"咪就係出兵！再養兵就等俾敵軍玩滲透將你由內擊潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養兵、練兵、建造兵器，做咗三四日，兩大據點物資起碼足夠打一兩日仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定好攻堅目標，罷住條馬路冇柒用，要有明確目標！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後喺據點周圍設置防線，將戰線+哨站一併推出據點以外確保城池<br />\n保證物資輸送路線，將兵器帶往戰線<br />\n廣發英雄帖，遍地開花，聲東擊西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連接各地戰場，一方有難，定必八方支援！<br />\n周末將至，人手更充裕，正是起兵良日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6f3f9e9b1c1da7bb04a00aa2f0044ec6c3ec7","tid":1723313,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"廿連"},{"pid":"23768795c390edcd3e80459c359093047e8fba91","tid":1723313,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a28b2ac02689d4231cd914ff2670b119db37c1","tid":1723313,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"aac5029c320ab990296d7ef644a7b576181ba27b","tid":1723313,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"出兵狗宿"},{"pid":"fab541dc65c0fe8c3908adf41ae3804bdcc8600c","tid":1723313,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6ac889cb18839683d2c099c5e2914547ef32e763","tid":1723313,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco